### Welcome to the project page of OSUE-TUWien.
This project page hosts libraries used for the OSUE lecture at the Vienna University of Technology.

### sem182
Our semaphore library.

### SE
Our sequencer/eventcounter library

### Authors and Contributors
This project page is currently maintained by Benedikt Huber (@visq) and Roland Kammerer (@rck).
